headline: Is ADM Still Attractive After a 17.5% Year to Date Rally in 2025?
summary: Wondering if Archer-Daniels-Midland is quietly turning into a value opportunity while everyone looks elsewhere? Here is a closer look at what the recent share price and fundamentals are really telling us. ADM's stock has slipped 2.8% over the last week but is still up 3.6% over the past month, which suggests some short term volatility.
